  <body>
    <div class="page-wrapper">
      <br />
      <div class="page">
        <div class="page-content">
          <h2>Cancellation Policy for Digital Products</h2>
          <p>
            Thanks for purchasing our products at Panorah.in operated by
            Panorah.
          </p>
          <p>
            We offer a cancellation of order for all purchases made on our
            website or any other sales channels. If you are not satisfied with
            the product that you have purchased from us, you can cancel the
            order and opt for a refund. You are eligible for a full
            reimbursement within 14 calendar days of your purchase.
          </p>
          <p>
            After the 14-day period you will no longer be eligible and won't be
            able to cancel the order. We encourage our customers to try the
            product (or service) in the first two weeks after their purchase to
            ensure it fits your needs. All the refunds after cancellation, as
            per the price of the product, will be returned in currency INR as
            per today's rate.
          </p>
          <p>
            If you have any additional questions or would like to request a
            refund, feel free to contact us at <a
              href="mailto:inquiry.panorah@gmail.com"
              >inquiry.panorah@gmail.com</a
            >.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
      <br />
    </div>
